beer.beer_description:
Tonic is our new release for Summer 2016/17. 
Tonic is ambidextrous. You can drink it straight up as a refreshing Summer Witbier with its array of botanicals (orange peel, juniper berries, lemon myrtle, coriander and cinchona bark), or use it as a tonic mixer by adding a shot of your favourite gin. We recommend the citrus forward craft gin from Baker Williams (Mudgee). Cucumber garnish optional. 
First brewed in 2014 with Wheaty Brewing Corps, Adelaide (AU) & Yeastie Boys, UK / NZ. This version is amplified.
Enjoy this refreshing summer witbier with its balanced botanicals or use it as the perfect tonic to bring your favourite gin to life.
